Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_WFDSITS(zc) From W1HRMAT12
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_WFDSITS(zc) From W1HRMAT12
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_WFDSITS(zc) From W1HRMAT12
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_WFDSITS(zc) From W1HRMAT12
